descriptionHtml:
A farm in the wilderness of the Rift, home to a herd of uniquely-colored ponies.

Ponies are fully custom, from the textures of the amazing [url=http://www.slofslair.co.uk/index.php?page=modarticle&modarticle/id=629ux8cu9d1]AlienSlof[/url] ([url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/62287]Nexus Profile[/url]).  Ponies have the same stats as regular horses. 

Includes an unowned farmhouse with a bed and two non-respawning containers.

[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=9745][Steam Workshop][/url]

/********Install*************/
Copy [b]goldleafponyfarm.esp[/b] and [b]GoldleafPonyFarm.bsa[/b] to your Skyrim/Data directory and enable goldleafponyfarm.esp in \"Data Files\"


/********Uninstall***********/
Remove [b]goldleafponyfarm.esp[/b] and [b]GoldleafPonyFarm.bsa[/b] from your Skyrim/Data directory.


/********Credit**************/
All credit for pony textures goes to [url=http://www.slofslair.co.uk]AlienSlof[/url].  My saddle texture replacement (NOT INCLUDED, but shown in images) is sedryn\'s [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3200]Ornate Saddles[/url]


/********Updates*************/
Update v1.1 (2.11.12): Ponies are now invulnerable so they won\'t die to errant dragons~ They also will no longer turn on you if you accidentally attack them or other wildlife.

Update v1.2 (2.13.12): Fixed the navmesh on the farmhouse so you don\'t end up stuck in the porch upon exiting while having a follower
